        public AlertEvent​(CharSequence alertId,
                  CharSequence sensorId,
                  CharSequence equipmentId,

                  Double temperature,
                  Double threshold,
                  CharSequence location,
                  AlertSeverity severity,
                  CharSequence message,
                  Boolean acknowledged)
        All-args constructor.
        Parameters:
        alertId - Unique alert identifier
        sensorId - Sensor that triggered the alert
        equipmentId - Equipment associated with the sensor
        timestamp - When the alert was generated
        temperature - Temperature value that triggered alert
        threshold - Threshold that was exceeded
        location - Location of the sensor
        severity - Severity level of the alert
        message - Human readable alert message
        acknowledged - Whether alert has been acknowledged
